properties.areaDesc: Ontonagon to Upper Entrance of Portage Canal MI; Black River To Ontonagon MI; Saxon Harbor WI to Black River MI; Upper Entrance of Portage Canal to Eagle River MI
properties.headline: Small Craft Advisory issued January 13 at 10:26PM EST until January 15 at 4:00AM EST by NWS Marquette MI
properties.description:
* WHAT...West winds 15 to 25 kt with gusts up to 35 kt and waves
5 to 8 feet expected.

* WHERE...Saxon Harbor WI to Black River MI, Black River to
Ontonagon MI, Ontonagon to Upper Entrance of Portage Canal MI
and Upper Entrance of Portage Canal to Eagle River MI.

* WHEN...From 10 AM EST /9 AM CST/ Tuesday to 4 AM EST /3 AM
CST/ Wednesday.

* IMPACTS...Conditions will be hazardous to small craft.
properties.instruction:
Inexperienced mariners, especially those operating smaller
vessels, should avoid navigating in hazardous conditions.

NWSheadline: SMALL CRAFT ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM 10 AM EST /9 AM CST/ TUESDAY TO 4 AM EST /3 AM CST/ WEDNESDAY
